entry.title: Ukraine's Eastern Advance Puts Forces Close to Key Town
entry.content: Images of the Ukrainian flag being raised over local government buildings and residents greeting soldiers with tears of joy have boosted morale across the country after months on the defensive.

entry.title: King Charles's Reign Dawns as Britain Mourns Its Queen
entry.content: King Charles III will address the British people for the first time as their new monarch, as the nation begins to observe a period of national mourning following the death of Queen Elizabeth II.
